      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i had a small cyst removed by my doctor a few days ago and the cut area is looking a bit red and feels kind of warm to the touch. there's also a bit of yellow stuff oozing out of it. is that normal or should i be worried? i've got some antiseptic cream at home i could just put on it?",
