      "content": "thanks. i dont really have a fever or anything, it's just localized to the cut. i really dont want to go back to the clinic and pay for another appointment just for this. if i just keep doing the warm compress and applying the cream every few hours, do you think it'll clear itself up in a day or two? i'm sure it's fine as long as i keep it clean.",
